{"tid":391052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首：警務處獲公眾形象獎銀獎　顯示警隊不怕被抹黑","createTime":"2017-09-07T13:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T01:12:27.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a14932ec4671babf00802e4e1a937089fb7e94da","tid":391052,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，會兌現競選政綱承諾，在不影響公眾利益下，簡政放權，訂立清晰工作目標和行事指引，為公務員工作減壓。她在公務員獎勵計劃活動致辭時，特別表揚渠務署、警務處和消防處三個部門。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥讚揚消防人員，在危難時拯救生命，值得尊重，所以獲公眾形象獎金獎多年，她任職社署署長時帶領的社署，也不能挑戰金獎，只能獲得銀獎。至於警務處獲得公眾形象獎銀獎，顯示警隊不怕被抹黑。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，渠務署獲獎的地下蓄洪池項目，正是她出任發展局局長時提出的項目，在落實計劃過程，體現敢於創新、膽識和勇氣。<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1352873_1_L_20170907201225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1352873_1_L_20170907201225.jpg&h=1544e980&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abbde1dff4876413860a2f398e70d8f4050ea5c0","tid":391052,"uid":11001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公務員獎勵計劃</blockquote><br />\n同CCTVB圍威喂選港姐有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338765acd96a934c3a80e8cc4c99bf10e4e4ed4c","tid":391052,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公務員獎勵計劃</blockquote><br />\n同CCTVB圍威喂選港姐有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好唔同<br />\n港姐要面向公眾<br />\n公務員獎勵計劃同閂埋房門打飛機一樣"},{"pid":"8162881b6f1dd8fb5fac9d1977b0dde6f6728bfc","tid":391052,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公務員獎勵計劃</blockquote><br />\n同CCTVB圍威喂選港姐有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同孔子和平獎果D差不多"},{"pid":"716fce8aded2f5dcf8125f5265fa6ea13bcd6e46","tid":391052,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:57:46.000Z","msg":"本身都黑咪唔怕抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2419330ae2ce130e92879852ff5bc01f279f8a7","tid":391052,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身都黑咪唔怕抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2da31df7498f0863290143967b29593e9ff8421","tid":391052,"uid":100626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f45e0d0315b8192655057e29422e7374724640a","tid":391052,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:15:08.000Z","msg":"我我我我我我我我我"},{"pid":"01f1b8fdbdd661c54f25cc9b172763a0ea59e51e","tid":391052,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:17:08.000Z","msg":"黑既點抹都係黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8a2a2d859377843e13c2995518dc79dbb3c4a0","tid":391052,"uid":132770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"委任銀奬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由委任特首頒發"},{"pid":"cc80470c15eb00438db0a84e29f187062659c9fb","tid":391052,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T00:20:30.000Z","msg":"自己頒俾自己,真係好有公信力"},{"pid":"cc4d6212eb883eb85437e9f072109dc96d21e611","tid":391052,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T01:12:27.000Z","msg":"英國研究，中國製造，南韓起源，匪隊聲譽"}]}